---
title: Quick Spiced Chicken & Currant Couscous with Yoghurt & Toasted Almonds
description: Couscous — the grain so nice they named it twice! Here we’ve added sweet currants and nutty almonds for a pop of
flavour, and topped the whole thing off with mildly spiced chicken strips and greens. Don’t forget the generous dollop of
cooling yoghurt to bring the meal together.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
